The repository, Library_Management is consisting of 4 files with names (Book.java, BookCatalog.java, BookStatus.java, BookManagementUI.java)
The BookManagementUI.java consists of the main method, the execution needs to be done on that file.
Challenges:
1. Choosing the Data Structure for storing and for operations like Searching, Updating, Deletion
2. An enumeration class has been created to overcome the challenge faced of creating an instance, and also as status is a property of Book using a class is more understandable.
